## ERROR TIPS

### Burner mining drill and inserter output blocked
- The burner mining drill and inserter are waiting for space in the destination. Ensure that the destination chest has enough space to receive the iron ore. If the chest is full, the mining drill and inserter will stop working. Place more chests or expand the storage area.

### Errors when using extracting but being too far
 -  Make sure to move to the target entity where you want to extract from before extracting items
